for structured version of pythonANN_coupling:

all code (i.e. py modules, shared lib, .h, .o, .c) is kept in a subdirectory ./pythonANN w.r.t fortran executable

in ./pythonANN: build shared library via 'python builder.py'
                enable runtime linking of shared lib via 'install_name_tool -id "@rpath/libplugin.dylib" libplugin.dylib'

in ./ : 	compile fortran executable with linked shared library via 'gfortran -o run_test -L ./pythonANN/ -lplugin test_pythonANN.f90'
                enable runtime linking of shared lib via 'install_name_tool -change libplugin.dylib @loader_path/pythonANN/libplugin.dylib run_test'
                                                     and 'install_name_tool -add_rpath @loader_path/pythonANN/ run_test'
